 make thirty\u2013eight appearances and scoring three times in all competitions.\n\nIn the 2016 season, Shoji started the season when he helped Kashima Antlers kept two clean sheets in the first two league matches of the season.<ref>{{cite news|title=G\u5927\u962a\u3001\u65b0\u30b9\u30bf\u516c\u5f0f\u6226\u521d\u6226\u306f\u9ed2\u661f\u2026\u4ea4\u4ee3\u7b56\u7684\u4e2d\u306e\u9e7f\u5cf6\u304c\u767d\u661f\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u30c8|url=https://www.soccer-king.jp/news/japan/jl/20160228/405992.html|publisher=Soccer King|language=Japanese|date=28 February 2016|accessdate=28 March 2020}}<br>{{cite news|url=https://www.so-net.ne.jp/antlers/sp/games/51727/match_review|title=\uff12\uff10\uff11\uff16\u660e\u6cbb\u5b89\u7530\u751f\u547d\uff2a\uff11\u30ea\u30fc\u30b0\u3000\uff11\uff53\uff54\u30b9\u30c6\u30fc\u30b8 \u7b2c2\u7bc0 \u30b5\u30ac\u30f3\u9ce5\u6816\u6226|publisher=Kashima Antlers|language=Japanese|date=5 March 2016|accessdate=28 March 2020}}</ref> Since the start of the season, Shoji continued to regain his first team place, playing in the centre\u2013back position.<ref>{{cite news|title=\u67cf \u5947\u8de1\u7684V\u5b57\u56de\u5fa9\u30012\u4f4d\u9e7f\u5cf6\u6483\u7834\u3067\u516c\u5f0f\u62265\u9023\u52dd!!\u300c\u3053\u306e\u307e\u307e\u52dd\u3061\u7d9a\u3051\u305f\u3044\u300d|url=https://web.gekisaka.jp/news/detail/?188047-188047-fl|publisher=Web Gekisaka|language=Japanese|date=24 April 2016|accessdate=28 March 2020}}<br>{{cite web|url=https://www.so-net.ne.jp/antlers/games/51834/live|title=\uff12\uff10\uff11\uff16\uff2a\u30ea\u30fc\u30b0\u30e4\u30de\u30b6\u30ad\u30ca\u30d3\u30b9\u30b3\u30ab\u30c3\u30d7 \u30b0\u30eb\u30fc\u30d7\u30b9\u30c6\u30fc\u30b8 \u7b2c5\u7bc0|publisher=Kashima Antlers|language=Japanese|date=18 May 2016|accessdate=28 March 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325193845/https://www.so-net.ne.jp/antlers/games/51834/live|archivedate=28 March 2020|url-status=dead}}<br>{{cite web|url=https://www.so-net.ne.jp/antlers/games/51786|title=\uff1